data.description: Take advantage of this assumable loan!!!!16 years remaining at 3.875% with a balance of $146000. Mortgage payment is $1030.18  Loan is tranferrable to a qualified buyer.   Enjoy the breath-taking views South from the 48th floor and take in Lake Michigan, the city skyline, Navy Pier and the night sky. Enter into a hall foyer with walls of closets , large living room, dining area that fits a large table. The kitchen with granite counter tops and SS appliances. The large bedroom easily fits a king size bed and large closet. This is a full-amenity building which includes 24-hour door staff, fitness center, package room, outdoor Jr Olympic pool, cabanas, grills, basketball court, party room, theater room, laundry room,  a dry cleaners. Monthly Garage Parking available on-site.   Assessments include heat, air, water and internet & Cable.  Very clean and freshly pinted with neutral colors,nothing to do just move in.
